<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752056>
    dc:description "Map 3: Distributions of Heteromeringia apholisapholis sp. n., H. zophinazophina sp. n., H. decora sp. n., H. nervosanervosa sp. n., H. volcanavolcana sp. n., H. nanellananella sp. n., H. nigrifrons KERTESZ, and H. fucata HENDEL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752056/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4751972>
    dc:description "Fig. 8: Heteromeringia czernyi KERTESZ, left lateral with detail of anepisternum and arrow indicating diagnostic upturned bristle. Fig. 9: H. fumipennisfumipennis MELANDER & ARGO, anepisternum with arrow indicating diagnostic lateral disc." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4751972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752012>
    dc:description "Figs 34-35: Heteromeringia czernyi KERTESZ, internal genitalia, basiphallus shaded. 34 anterior; 35 left lateral. Ejaculatory apodeme omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752012/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752028>
    dc:description "Figs 48-50: Female internal genitalia (spermathecae and ventral receptacle). 48 Heteromeringia czernyi KERTESZ; 49 H. flavifronsflavifrons HENNIG; 50 H. lateralis sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752028/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752008>
    dc:description "Figs 31-33: Heteromeringia czernyi KERTESZ, external terminalia. 31 left lateral; 32 posterior; 33 right surstylus, left lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752022>
    dc:description "Figs 42-44: Heteromeringia mediana sp. n., genitalia. 42 internal, left lateral; 43 external, left lateral; 44 external, posterior. Ejaculatory apodeme omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752022/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752026>
    dc:description "Figs 45-47: Heteromeringia quadriseta sp. n., genitalia. 45 internal, left lateral; 46 external, left lateral; 47 external, posterior. Ejaculatory apodeme omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752026/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4751962>
    dc:description "Fig. 1: Agonistic interaction between Heteromeringia nitidaZZ OHNSON males (South Carolina)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4751962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

